│ THOUGHT: After extensive analysis and multiple attempts, I have correctly   │
│ identified the root cause of the LLVM crash as a dominance violation in the │
│ SLP vectorizer's postponed gathers emission logic. The issue occurs because │
│ non-PHI gather instructions are placed using                                │
│ `Builder.SetInsertPoint(PrevVec)` which doesn't guarantee dominance over    │
│ all users.                                                                  │
│                                                                             │
